flowchart TB
  S[Need Excalidraw help] --> A[Setup: check_env + self_test]
  A --> Q{Task type}

  Q --> B1[Embed in app]
  Q --> B2[API or scene edits]
  Q --> B3[Mermaid to scene]
  Q --> B4[Library merge]
  Q --> B5[Account import]

  B1 --> R1[Read install reference]
  B2 --> R2[Read API reference]
  B3 --> R3[Run mermaid_to_scene]
  B4 --> R4[Run library_merge]
  B5 --> R5[Run import_to_excalidraw headed]

  R1 --> V[Validate result]
  R2 --> V
  R3 --> V
  R4 --> V
  R5 --> V

  V --> O[Deliver output + risks]
